# Exploration: sed

## Rounds
  round 0: 33 isolated cumulative, 38 identical in round (single-phase)

## Observed: 22/24 flags
  4 solo, 18 via combination
  2 additional error-differentiated
  3 behavioral aliases detected

## Solo (unique behavior)
  --debug
    exemplar: "--debug" "input.txt" in alpha_minimal (different)
    base:
    flag:
      SED PROGRAM:
        i\nput.txt
  --follow-symlinks
    exemplar: "--follow-symlinks" "input.txt" "other.txt" in alpha_minimal (-2 lines)
    base:
      nput.txt
      hello world
    flag:
      nput.txt
      hello world
  --in-place
    exemplar: "--in-place" "input.txt" "other.txt" in alpha_minimal (different)
    base:
      nput.txt
      hello world
    flag:
  --posix
    exemplar: "--posix" "$(head -n1 input.txt)" "input.txt" in numeric_standard / input.txt=size:1 (+1 lines, exit 1→0)
    base:
    flag:
  -i
    exemplar: "-i" "input.txt" "other.txt" in alpha_minimal (different)
    base:
      nput.txt
      hello world
    flag:
  -l
    exemplar: "-l" "input.txt" in alpha_minimal (different)
    base:
    flag:

